graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks Component<br/>Workbench & Runtime Images]

    %% External Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|base images| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.11/3.12<br/>registry.access.redhat.com<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|GPU support| CUDA[CUDA Base 12.6/12.8<br/>quay.io/rhoai/cuda-*<br/>Conditional]
    Notebooks -->|GPU support| ROCm[ROCm Base 6.2/6.4<br/>quay.io/rhoai/rocm-*<br/>Conditional]
    Notebooks -->|notebook UI| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x<br/>Conditional]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x<br/>Conditional]
    Notebooks -->|XAI toolkit| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Toolkit<br/>Conditional]
    Notebooks -->|LLM tools| LLMCompressor[LLMCompressor<br/>Conditional]
    Notebooks -->|CLI tools| OpenShiftClient[OpenShift CLI oc<br/>Required]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller] -->|launches pods| Notebooks
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|queries images| Notebooks
    Pipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines] -->|executes tasks| Notebooks
    ImageStreams[OpenShift ImageStreams] -->|references| Notebooks

    %% Integration Points
    Notebooks -->|references| ImageStreams
    Notebooks -.->|workbench pods| NotebookController
    Notebooks -.->|UI display| Dashboard
    Notebooks -.->|runtime execution| Pipelines

    %% Build System Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|built by| Konflux[Konflux CI/CD<br/>Multi-arch builds]
    Notebooks -->|stored in| Quay[Quay.io Registry<br/>quay.io/opendatahub]
    Konflux -->|source from| GitHub[GitHub<br/>red-hat-data-services/notebooks]

    %% External Services
    Notebooks -->|data access| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Model artifacts, datasets]
    Notebooks -->|packages| PyPI[PyPI.org<br/>Python packages]

